Recent Developments in Gene Therapy for Homozygous Familial 
Hypercholesterolemia.

Ajufo E(1), Cuchel M(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Medicine, Division of Translational Medicine and Human 
Genetics, Perelman School of Medicine, University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia, 
